product_name: Fresh organic russet potato, premium fruits and produce vegitable, Gluten free 10lbs
description: Despite the popular misconception that potatoes are fattening, baked potatoes can be used as part of a healthy diet

latest_reviews.reviewTitle: Best potatoes I have seen in a long time
latest_reviews.reviewBody: WOW! These potatoes are huge, beautiful bakers. I planned on canning these, but just have to save out some to cook in our wood cook stove.  I have not see potatoes this nice in many years. Living in the UP, I often think we get dregs or left over produce. Organic is hard to find up here, and often the quality is not worth purchasing.  I have just ordered 2 more of these.
after buying these potatoes I see no evidence that they are certified organic

I've purchased potatoes from other companies and they were for the most part, sub-par. One time they arrived as nothing but mush. These Potatoes are as near perfect as I have ever seen, clean no real bemishes and the taste is Great.
All the potatoes were a similar medium size and had very few blemishes. Delicious as air fried fries.
Had to throw away. Just tasted terrible
